{"ts":"2026-07-13T10:35:48.048Z","author":"codex-sdk-wide-20260713","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/3","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-13T10:35:48.048Z","author":"codex-sdk-wide-20260713","text":"Final local evidence: release gates passed build, typecheck, docs/skills, strict static quality, package boundary, token budgets, exact coverage (279 files, 5,604 tests, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines), version sync, secrets, packed npx smoke (12 packages), and 88-command package-first dogfood. Manual packed temp consumer /tmp/pm-sdk-manual-ujCqZK verified direct runFiles/runDocs/runDeps, PmClient readback, and active/historical/sentinel classification. Sentry/telemetry gate: critical=0, high=0 over 14 days; health warnings=0; history drift=0. Pre-commit release:gates stopped only at the Greptile review gate because review requires committed changes; it will be rerun on the PR head."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-13T10:35:48.048Z"}],"before_hash":"6d41f64f50489e68fcb768d62d06972669a634587036c4103bd87a0ff6ce719c","after_hash":"8ba3f911f15c89b0533790405a111758f2c2daa7e3390270c39d54ff0c708764"}
