{"ts":"2026-07-13T10:45:29.820Z","author":"codex-sdk-wide-20260713","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/4","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-13T10:45:29.820Z","author":"codex-sdk-wide-20260713","text":"Greptile preflight review 79d26578-e567-4bfb-9aa6-9837c2c8eb3f: accepted both P2 findings. Preserved backward-compatible dangling_reference_count as active+terminal total while active_dangling_reference_count remains the warning/gating signal; documented the contract and updated assertions. Changed the collector test to import the public SDK module directly. Verification: focused deps+validate 97/97, strict static quality, package boundary, token budget, and docs/skills gates pass."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-13T10:45:29.820Z"}],"before_hash":"3f317ef4a95a83dc475d433846f5f2dbe79b69c8725de0825204b40769298338","after_hash":"60a9e8f1d594de976276e7ccb8527c0f82e269cc845f47283091d6264efaf4bd"}
{"ts":"2026-07-13T11:13:04.126Z","author":"codex-sdk-wide-20260713","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/5","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-13T11:13:04.126Z","author":"codex-sdk-wide-20260713","text":"Hosted review round 1 implementation evidence: fixed files-discover apply race reporting so only newly committed links count as added/changed; bounded relative-path scanning to 32 KiB while retaining full absolute-path discovery; parallelized file probes; replaced resource-result double casts with a typed mapped result; and hardened dependency governance against malformed non-string runtime targets. Focused files/docs/deps suite passes 40/40 with typecheck."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-13T11:13:04.126Z"}],"before_hash":"60a9e8f1d594de976276e7ccb8527c0f82e269cc845f47283091d6264efaf4bd","after_hash":"0cacabc3976e8d96863f7445cf21106406704d8b9e6f2813a7cfa2b29fb96329"}
{"ts":"2026-07-13T11:44:09.626Z","author":"codex-sdk-wide-20260713","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/6","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-13T11:44:09.625Z","author":"codex-sdk-wide-20260713","text":"Hosted review round 2 evidence: accepted Gemini cleanup by removing a redundant runtime string type guard and the artificial malformed-match test; also removed the now-exposed impossible regex match fallback. Greptile's P1 export claim was disproven against the built package declaration: dist/sdk/index.d.ts already re-exports FilesCommandOptions, FilesResult, DocsCommandOptions, DocsResult, DepsCommandOptions, and DepsResult through runtime.js. Verification: 159 focused tests, typecheck, strict quality, and full 5,604/5,604 coverage at exact 100/100/100/100."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-13T11:44:09.626Z"}],"before_hash":"0cacabc3976e8d96863f7445cf21106406704d8b9e6f2813a7cfa2b29fb96329","after_hash":"543db09b94e797ac00df325de9006801783807d6f1c7c8b731955e1835b0901d"}
{"ts":"2026-07-13T12:00:06.827Z","author":"codex-sdk-wide-20260713","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/7","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-13T12:00:06.827Z","author":"codex-sdk-wide-20260713","text":"Hosted review round 3 evidence: accepted two late Gemini findings. Dependency governance now ignores null/non-object legacy dependency entries and defaults missing kinds to related without any, while files discovery tracks applied candidate indices to avoid redundant path-key resolution for skipped results. Verification: focused 40/40, typecheck, strict static/package-boundary/token gates, and full 5,604/5,604 at exact 100/100/100/100."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-13T12:00:06.827Z"}],"before_hash":"543db09b94e797ac00df325de9006801783807d6f1c7c8b731955e1835b0901d","after_hash":"26640124010252db1835a52e60e56e1cfeb0abaaf9e83e446296f372a969356b"}
{"ts":"2026-07-13T12:31:20.390Z","author":"codex-sdk-wide-20260713","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/8","value":{"created_at":"2026-07-13T12:31:20.390Z","author":"codex-sdk-wide-20260713","text":"Hosted review round 4 evidence: accepted CodeRabbit's self-contained SDK example, source-aware blocker remediation, and strict closed-versus-terminal compatibility count findings. Dependency summary mode now counts unique nodes, edges, and missing targets with a cycle-safe traversal without constructing exponential tree/graph payloads; explicit max-depth remains available while the default preserves complete graph semantics. Verification: focused deps+validate 98/98, typecheck, strict static/package-boundary/token/docs-link gates, and full 5,605/5,605 coverage at exact 100/100/100/100 (35,469 statements; 25,429 branches; 7,166 functions; 34,690 lines)."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-13T12:31:20.390Z"}],"before_hash":"26640124010252db1835a52e60e56e1cfeb0abaaf9e83e446296f372a969356b","after_hash":"48613bcceadd92dc93f1b9cd69009cc5a7ca1e29f438e19ce52d57ecd75273b9"}
